    "description": "Gloo is manageable early but not oppressive until he can reliably stack Sticky and access his attach for long skirmishes/picks. He peaks in mid-game teamfights where his CC, sustain healing from Goo detonations, and damage transfer disrupt cores; late game he remains strong but is more countered by coordinated focus/anti-heal and higher burst."
